Why Work With The Ramage Law Group?

  • Decades of Experience: Led by Sharon Ramage, a former social worker and prosecutor with over 30 years of legal expertise.
  • Specialized Advocacy: Unique focus on special education law and navigating family transitions for children with disabilities.
  • Strategic Results: We handle complex, high-conflict cases with a roadmap designed to protect your familys future.
  • Local Roots: Deeply familiar with the Collin, Denton, and Tarrant County court systems.
